<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>SkyLearn Infrastructure Dashboard</title>

<style>

body{
    margin:0;
    padding:40px;
    background:#0f172a;
    color:#f8fafc;
    font-family:Segoe UI,Arial,sans-serif;
}

.container{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:auto;
}

.card{
    background:#1e293b;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:30px;
    box-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
}

h1{
    color:#38bdf8;
    margin-top:0;
}

.subtitle{
    color:#cbd5e1;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

table{
    width:100%;
    border-collapse:collapse;
}

td{
    padding:12px;
    border-bottom:1px solid #334155;
}

td:first-child{
    width:280px;
    color:#38bdf8;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.status{
    color:#22c55e;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.footer{
    margin-top:25px;
    text-align:center;
    color:#94a3b8;
    font-size:14px;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<h1>SkyLearn Infrastructure Dashboard</h1>

<p class="subtitle">
This server is managed using <strong>Ansible Automation</strong>.
</p>

<table>

<tr>
<td>Hostname</td>
<td>{{ ansible_hostname }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Administrator</td>
<td>{{ admin_user }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Operating System</td>
<td>{{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Kernel Version</td>
<td>{{ ansible_kernel }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Python Version</td>
<td>{{ ansible_python.version.major }}.{{ ansible_python.version.minor }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Web Server</td>
<td>{{ web_service }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Web Package</td>
<td>{{ web_package }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Deployment Directory</td>
<td>{{ skylearn_root }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Deployment Date</td>
<td>{{ ansible_date_time.date }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Deployment Time</td>
<td>{{ ansible_date_time.time }}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Infrastructure Status</td>
<td class="status">🟢 Healthy</td>
</tr>

</table>

<div class="footer">

Provisioned using

<strong>Ansible Roles</strong> •
<strong>Jinja2 Templates</strong> •
<strong>Variables</strong> •
<strong>Handlers</strong> •
<strong>Firewalld</strong>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
